gloss.term:
Level of the realization of a bodhisattva;
                                according to the general Mahāyāna, there are ten bodhisattva levels; according to Vajrayāna,
                                thirteen.

The name of Buddha’s wife as found in some
                                texts, including the Lalitavistara;
                                the name of Buddha's tantric consort.

A Buddhist deity; the name of a bodhisattva;
                                also the name of the deity asking Vajrasattva questions at the time
                                of the delivery of the CMT.
